<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        h1,
        h2 {
            color: #333131;
            font-size: 20px;
            padding: 6px 0px;
        }

        p {
            color: #494747;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .container,
        .content {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            padding:
                10px 20px;
        }

        .header {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-rows: 1fr;
            padding:
                10px 20px;
            margin: 5px 0px;
            background-color: #66f5f5;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .header h2 {
            color: #140b64;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- header -->
        <div class="header">
            <h2>Virtual Campus Recruitment</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Greetings Recruiter</h2>
            <p>Your recruiter account for {{company_name}} has been successfully created on virtual campus recruitment, at
                {{time}}.
            </p>
            <br>
            <p>Now to create and manage various jobs at
                campus and avail our other services, your account needs to be email verified.
                For now, your account stands as unverified and will be verified by our system administrators. Once
                verified,
                company and
                recruiters can create jobs on our system. Verification process will be completed within next 48hrs.
            </p>
            <br />
            <p>If you haven't created this account, please contact us back immediately. For any queries or issues, please contact us using this email.
            </p>
            <br />
            <p>Visit our website anytime, anywhere at
                <a style="color: #223891;" href="https://campus-recruitment-system-rust.vercel.app">Virtual Campus
                    Recruitment</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>